com.revature.GSQL.GSQL

Class GSQL

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revature.GSQL.GSQL.GSQL

  • public class GSQL
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which serves as the public face for Greatest SQL. Contains methods to add a metamodel, add to database, retrieve from database, and make Transactions(commit, savepoint,rollback). Must use the 'getInstance' method to get an instance of the class before using any of its methods.
